cppnanomsg: C++ binding for nanomsg library
-------------------------------------------

To build:

1. git clone git@github.com:nanomsg/cppnanomsg.git
2. cd cppnanomsg
4. mkdir build
5. cd build
6. cmake ..
7. make
8. make test
9. sudo make install

Alternatively, given that the binding consists of a single header file,
rather than installing it, you can avoid dependency and make nn.hpp part
of your project.


